*Zahvalan* sam što je postojala mogućnost da vidim tu prekrasnu prirodu. (I am grateful that there was an opportunity to see this beautiful nature.)

*Zahvalna* sam roditeljima što su me podržali. (I am thankful to my parents for supporting me.)

Primila sam *zahvalan* pogled od starijeg gospodina. (I got a grateful look from the elderly gentleman.)

Osećam se *zahvalnom* za sve što mi je dano. (I feel thankful for all that has been given to me.)

On je dao *zahvalan* osmesak. (He gave a grateful smile.)